name: Luo Chuan - Fiat Lux - CYC  Collections

metadata.name: Fiat Lux #1
metadata.description: I dreamed to be a theoretical physicist when I was a child. And as a photographer, I became even more fascinated by the irreproducible moments of time, space, and the uniqueness. This series is the symbol of the beginning of the universe that is full of the beauty, uncertainty, and irreproducibility.
